title  : Gem Wedge Plugin
suite  : rubyworks
summary: Safe Gem Loading
contact: trans <transfire@gmail.com>
authors: Thomas Sawyer
license: Apache 2.0
created: 2010-07-21

description:
  The Gem Wedge plugin turns the Gem load wedge provided by
  the `wedge` gem into a RubyGem plugin, so it is automatically
  loaded whenever RubyGems is loaded.

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/wedge
  repo: git://github.com/rubyworks/gem-wedge.git

